# Local runtime state written by RagnarOrchestrator -- letta_agents.json is the
# only .ragnar/ file meant to be tracked (the provisioning manifest); everything
# else here is per-machine run history/logs/checkpoints that should never be
# committed.
.ragnar/run_ledger.jsonl
.ragnar/approvals.jsonl
.ragnar/memory_writebacks.jsonl
.ragnar/agent_transcripts.jsonl
.ragnar/orchestrator.sqlite
.ragnar/runs/
.ragnar/pr_drafts/
.ragnar/worktrees/

.venv/
__pycache__/
*.pyc
.pytest_cache/
*.egg-info/
